item.title: How do i input things? once ive changed the txt in folders?
item.dc:creator: @mehaku mehaku
item.description:
@mehaku wrote:

just double click run&compile, if you dont have one, right click on one of your .bat files and click edit, paste this over what is in there:

@echo off COLOR 08 title Cowscape Client "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin\java.exe" server pause
if you dont have version 7 replace the 7s with 6s and that should work, if you dont have java- download it (GUH!) LOL
